{"tid":632146,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【PUBG】技巧/冷知識 討論區","createTime":"2018-04-17T06:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T08:13:45.000Z","uid":180290,"like":4,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1bac98ac3c089dd829048e6e8e6f3461ac44fe","tid":632146,"uid":180290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:12:06.000Z","msg":"雖然pubg都出左好耐 但我諗未必個個都知道某d小技巧<br />\n所以大家可以分享一下<br />\n<br />\n由於我同對槍太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就唔講對槍要點壓槍個d<br />\n但有d基本知識/技巧都可以分享一下<br />\n<br />\n1. 移形換影(車上換槍)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/135345_b4c6544ae53ccfaa2693994e1cd94552.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F135345_b4c6544ae53ccfaa2693994e1cd94552.jpg&h=e146f874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/135345_70cb0c5ce6e3d2a134dafb10e40e956f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F135345_70cb0c5ce6e3d2a134dafb10e40e956f.jpg&h=81146c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係車上到 開你既物品欄 之後換槍<br />\n咁係落車既時候 就自動換左槍<br />\n當你與到人 可以減少落地換槍既時間<br />\n<br />\n2.飄移境界(加速)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/135723_fc99167f7e0b6d3f39bdf49e6d73b42f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F135723_fc99167f7e0b6d3f39bdf49e6d73b42f.jpg&h=1b652434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好簡單 按shift掣加速<br />\n<br />\n3.無敵擋箭牌<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/135847_6f7e1fff2a0e273e0706e201f72f1e52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F135847_6f7e1fff2a0e273e0706e201f72f1e52.jpg&h=50340e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任何既車輛 都只會爆炸一次<br />\n當爆炸左之後 就成為一個無堅不吹的擋箭牌<br />\n係決賽圈既時候 好有用<br />\n<br />\n4.走得快好世界<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/140139_ab1a208e79c1b7aa7de55269f610c0fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F140139_ab1a208e79c1b7aa7de55269f610c0fb.jpg&h=12b05df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收槍跑比拎槍跑快<br />\n<br />\n5.側身射個三家姐(側射)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/140238_07b51af77e451cc9fea345c683895c51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F140238_07b51af77e451cc9fea345c683895c51.jpg&h=459802fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按Q or E掣  <br />\n大大減少別人打中你的機會 (特別爆頭)<br />\n<br />\n6.情深一射<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/140407_fede7a1cb5780461fb5757132720b6eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F140407_fede7a1cb5780461fb5757132720b6eb.jpg&h=f2e11438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/140544_5bc6b0c85b1321226d24a65638f6973a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F140544_5bc6b0c85b1321226d24a65638f6973a.jpg&h=73692cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按shift掣 可以穩定射擊 但只得5秒....<br />\n<br />\n7.眼睛想旅行(睇死角位)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/140538_83af64a99528b3bbee335106fa19d101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F140538_83af64a99528b3bbee335106fa19d101.jpg&h=b8413ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按瞄準既時候 只要按住側身(Q or E)<br />\n可以睇到平時睇唔到既位<br />\n<br />\n8.食藥要準時<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/140757_2f19fcb71cdf45999eb90e1339678a73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F140757_2f19fcb71cdf45999eb90e1339678a73.jpg&h=3b8fc065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每隻藥都唔同時間 時間就睇圖<br />\n<br />\n9.瀨死唔落地<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/140905_ea7adcb89107c1a77a7a536d2caceff3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F140905_ea7adcb89107c1a77a7a536d2caceff3.jpg&h=e3dbd937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高空既時候開降落傘<br />\n不斷前後前後前後 維持速度40就可以<br />\n你想飛幾遠都得<br />\n<br />\n就係甘多住先<br />\n各界巴打仲有既話 分享一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖片來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rOAATlub_CM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrOAATlub_CM&d=W6bE0wLMMcqaOnwU1zJ0sE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=0e7c743f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rOAATlub_CM</a>"},{"pid":"85659bb0d0875daca14559bcf7e84c98927b7b99","tid":632146,"uid":34,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:14:03.000Z","msg":"D名....<br />\n甘你老"},{"pid":"ae74dbcbfa37bd3e418e0588b7c0f15b2d5c2965","tid":632146,"uid":31961,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">甘你老母</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7298d4345df1e2908a74ae9da03c688c0dfe4ab3","tid":632146,"uid":180290,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:15:14.000Z","msg":"咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3225059aa2178e83018efec5d55ed22960088098","tid":632146,"uid":2566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"係好玩，但～唉，太多外掛...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8fca4d42421cda1c7087accfba0533ff83f49b","tid":632146,"uid":180290,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3225059aa2178e83018efec5d55ed22960088098","tid":632146,"uid":2566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"係好玩，但～唉，